data.title: Love their Tostado's
data.text: We have been going there for years and have always had a good meal....although all we order are their tostados with chili Verde. They are tasty with considerable meat. They offer a salsa bar that is nice but I must say I have never cared by their salsa's much. But, I keep returning!  Staff though is not friendly and actually never have been. But, I still return :-)
